OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox reports from Preston
OL,8,FCrown Court
OL,10,FA woman has been jailed for trying to
OL,11,Fabduct a seven-month old baby from
OL,12,Foutside a shop whilst her mother's
OL,13,Fhead was turned.
OL,15,FThe incident happened in Blackpool
OL,16,Fjust before midday on 10 May 2025.
