OL,3,CWoman jailed for attempting to abduct
OL,4,Ca baby in broad daylight
OL,6,FPreston Crown Court heard Nicola
OL,7,FGoldrick, 51 walked up to the baby in
OL,8,Fher pram, which was outside her
OL,9,Fmother's shop on Central Drive,
OL,10,FBlackpool.
OL,12,FShe took off the brake and wheeled the
OL,13,Fpram away with the baby inside.
OL,15,FThe court heard the baby's mother,
OL,16,FSarah Smith had been working on her
OL,17,Fice cream store and had turned
OL,18,Fmomentarily to speak to a delivery
OL,19,Fdriver which is when Goldrick struck.
