OL,3,CWoman jailed for attempting to abduct
OL,4,Ca baby in broad daylight
OL,6,FThe baby's mother chased Nicolette
OL,7,FGoldrick, 51, and stopped her getting
OL,8,Faway.
OL,10,FThe court heard Goldrick said nothing
OL,11,Fand walked away.
OL,13,FShe returned to the area near the shop
OL,14,Flater that afternoon and was arrested
OL,15,Fby police.
OL,17,FShe verbally abused officers as they
OL,18,Fled her to the police van and once
OL,19,Finside the van, she spat at one of
OL,20,Fthem.
