OL,4,Ca baby in broad daylight
OL,6,FGoldrick pleaded guilty to child
OL,7,Fabduction and assaulting an emergency
OL,8,Fworker on 28 July 2025, at Preston
OL,9,FCrown Court.
OL,11,FAt the sentence hearing on 7 October
OL,12,F2025, the court heard a victim
OL,13,Fpersonal statement read out on behalf
OL,14,Fof the parents where they stated that
OL,15,Fthis incident was the worst day of
OL,16,Ftheir lives and something they would
OL,17,Fnever get over.
